Security (CRITICAL)
NEVER use os/exec с паролями → используй golang.org/x/crypto/ssh
NEVER хардкодить секреты в config → env vars only
NEVER 'unsafe-inline' в CSP → nonce-based CSP
ALWAYS валидация input, parameterized SQL, rate limiting на auth
Architecture
Backend: Разбивай handlers на доменные роутеры (не monolithic server.go)
Database: golang-migrate для версионирования (не CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS)
Errors: Централизованная обработка respondError(w, r, err) с traceID
Files: Разбивай >500 строк на модули
Testing
Backend: table-driven tests, testcontainers-go для интеграционных
Coverage target: 70% Go, 50% React
Mock external dependencies
Code Style
Go: golangci-lint, gofmt, godoc comments
TypeScript: ESLint + Prettier, strict mode, functional components
SQL: snake_case, индексы для частых запросов, transactions для multi-step
Common Pitfalls
❌ God Objects → ✅ Domain routers
❌ Magic numbers → ✅ Named constants
❌ Deep nesting → ✅ Helper functions
❌ Commented code → ✅ Remove or document
❌ Console.log → ✅ Proper logging
❌ any type → ✅ Proper interfaces
Quick Wins Priority
Security fixes (sshpass, CSP, secrets)
Architecture refactoring (server.go, migrations, errors)
Mobile improvements (refresh token, parallel uploads, EXIF)
Performance (Excel backend, virtualization)
Infrastructure (Dockerfile, docker-compose, tests)</content>
